Conclusion: On balance the British Isles folk compilation better preserves the intimacy, melodic storytelling, warm natural mastering and dynamic range I care about, and its thoughtful sequencing promises a more continuous listening experience than a career‑spanning greatest‑hits rock collection—so I choose the British Isles folk compilation and reject the Classic Rock/AOR greatest‑hits for the reasons above.

